{"tid":351632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大愛包容］Google辭退發表反平權言論員工","createTime":"2017-08-08T08:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T18:33:20.000Z","uid":60341,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21fc3c9ce8a3a3043f9dcf5b1e59c529dc59e0f9","tid":351632,"uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:20:39.000Z","msg":"A Google employee who wrote a controversial memo about workplace diversity has been fired, the BBC can confirm. <br />\nThe controversial memo broke the firm&rsquo;s code of conduct, Google&rsquo;s chief executive Sundar Pichai said on Monday in an email to employees.<br />\nThe memo, shared widely at the weekend, suggested there were fewer women at Google due to biological differences. <br />\nMr Pichai said the text crossed the line due to it &quot;advancing harmful gender stereotypes in our workplace&rdquo;. <br />\nEntitled Google&rsquo;s Ideological Echo Chamber, the paper argued that &quot;the abilities of men and women differ in part due to biological causes and that these differences may explain why we don't see equal representation of women in tech and leadership&rdquo;. <br />\nThe author wrote: &quot;We need to stop assuming that gender gaps imply sexism.&quot; <br />\nGoogle has not confirmed who the employee is, but US media reports name him as James Damore.<br />\nThe memo was quickly criticised by Google&rsquo;s head of diversity, Danielle Brown, but the author - whose identity has not been revealed by Google - later wrote that he had received &quot;many personal messages from fellow Googlers expressing their gratitude&rdquo;. <br />\nComments 'not OK'<br />\nIn his note to staff sent on Monday afternoon, Mr Pichai spoke at length about protecting free speech in Google&rsquo;s ranks, and that &quot;much of what was in that memo is fair to debate, regardless of whether a vast majority of Googlers disagree with it&rdquo;.  <br />\nBut he added: &quot;To suggest a group of our colleagues have traits that make them less biologically suited to that work is offensive and not OK. <br />\n&quot;It is contrary to our basic values and our Code of Conduct, which expects 'each Googler to do their utmost to create a workplace culture that is free of harassment, intimidation, bias and unlawful discrimination&rsquo;.&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-40859004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-40859004&d=DSj0j%2Fs1g7mKpXqlN9%2FFvjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=7afd238b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-40859004</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現代伏爾泰：你若不同意我的看法，我將誓死封殺你說話的權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0a9af9ca47c04586dd762609a9329ca595d0ab","tid":351632,"uid":54733,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:23:00.000Z","msg":"左膠最冇言論自由"},{"pid":"6a4a653087de608c880fb75492db2ffbff7ebca9","tid":351632,"uid":134215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"痴撚線公司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b92787d72677f083467bd2b8d2b7c569e2e355","tid":351632,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:26:55.000Z","msg":"左膠嘅言論自由係要佢地批准<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d38ad6f5981d8216a22e6257579041322896bc4","tid":351632,"uid":12853,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左膠最冇言論自由</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本質就係順我者倡 逆我者亡<br />\n迫人跟佢地自己的意見<br />\n文字獄的變化版"},{"pid":"fa146f66f5cdfa25c5563ef4a5b55f5113ff0554","tid":351632,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個世界只可以得一種聲音"},{"pid":"7cedef1c8d59fcca7a3d8672a0339a928799823d","tid":351632,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislik